Post-Match Reflections: Kahnle said, 'For it to all crash like that, it's just... I'll be thinking about this for a long time, I can tell you that. It just sucks that maybe I could have done something differently.'
Weaver said, 'Sometimes, you don't get on the right end of it, and you just tip your cap to some hitters who executed on fundamental baseball.'
Betts said, 'Don’t strike out, put one in play right there; you never know what’s going to happen.'
